OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,FA private nursery has admitted
OL,7,Fcorporate manslaughter over the death
OL,8,Fof a 14-month-old boy, who died after
OL,9,Fbeing suffocated while staff tried to
OL,10,Fput him to asleep.
OL,12,FToddler Noah Sibanda died at
OL,13,FFairytales Day Nursery in Dudley on 9
OL,14,FDecember 2022.
OL,16,FHe was tightly wrapped in a sleeping
OL,17,Fbag, physically restrained face down
OL,18,Fon a cushion, with a blanket over his
OL,19,Fhead and had a leg placed over him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
