PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,FCCTV showed nursery practitioner
OL,7,FKimberley Cookson, 23, appearing to
OL,8,Ftry to make him sleep when he did not
OL,9,Fwant to. After some time, staff
OL,10,Fnoticed he was not breathing, and the
OL,11,Femergency services were called.
OL,13,FNoah was pronounced dead at hospital.
OL,15,FFairytales Day Nursery Limited on
OL,16,FWednesday admitted corporate
OL,17,Fmanslaughter and a Health and Safety
OL,18,Fat Work Act offence at Wolverhampton
OL,19,FCrown Court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,FDirector and business owner Deborah
OL,7,FLatewood, 55, also admitted a Health
OL,8,Fand Safety at Work Act offence. She
OL,9,Fsaid she did not know children were
OL,10,Fbeing put down to sleep in this
OL,11,Fdangerous way.
OL,13,FNursery practitioner Kimberley
OL,14,FCookson, 23, previously pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto gross negligence manslaughter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
