PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,FAlex Johnson, from Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService, said: "This case has been
OL,8,Fdeeply distressing and represents
OL,9,Fevery parent's worst nightmare
OL,10,Fwhenever they leave their young child
OL,11,Fat a nursery.
OL,13,F"Noah Sibanda should have been safe in
OL,14,Fthe care of professionals entrusted
OL,15,Fwith his wellbeing. He lost his life
OL,16,Fas a result of reckless and dangerous
OL,17,Fsleeping practices which posed an
OL,18,Fobvious and serious risk of harm.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,F"The evidence in this case, including
OL,7,FCCTV footage and expert medical
OL,8,Ffindings, showed that Noah was placed
OL,9,Fto sleep in a way that severely
OL,10,Frestricted his ability to breathe and
OL,11,Fmove. The prosecution case was that
OL,12,Fthese practices created a suffocating
OL,13,Fenvironment, from which a 14-month-old
OL,14,Fchild, was clearly unable to escape.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,F"Fairytales Day Nursery Limited has
OL,7,Fnow accepted criminal responsibility
OL,8,Ffor the systemic failures that led to
OL,9,Fthis tragedy, and Deborah Latewood has
OL,10,Falso acknowledged that the failings
OL,11,Foccurred under her management and
OL,12,Foversight. Kimberley Cookson has also
OL,13,Ftaken responsibility for her harmful
OL,14,Factions.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774624293
OL,3,CNursery admits corporate manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter toddler suffocates to death
OL,6,F"Nursery providers have a fundamental
OL,7,Fduty to protect the children in their
OL,8,Fcare. This case underscores the
OL,9,Fdevastating consequences of what
OL,10,Fhappens when that duty is breached.
OL,11,FOur thoughts remain with Noah's
OL,12,Ffamily, who have endured an
OL,13,Funimaginable loss."
OL,15,FThe defendants will be sentenced at
OL,16,FWolverhampton Crown Court on 16 April.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
